lectivity, should generally be avoided in patients with bronchospastic diseases.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/292261/', '', 'Felodipine, Acetylsalicylic acid, Amlodipine, Nifedipine', 'Mometasone furoate, Umeclidinium, Aclidinium, Mometasone, Cromoglicic acid, Ipratropium, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 1767369485);
